---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Achillea Built">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl py-12 sm:py-16">

    <div class="mb-12 reveal">
      <h1 class="mb-6">About</h1>

      <p class="text-lg leading-8 max-w-2xl">
        Achillea Built was created to offer a more thoughtful approach to small-scale
        construction — where quality, clarity, and good judgment matter as much as
        speed.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6 max-w-2xl reveal">
      <p class="leading-7">
        Many homeowners find themselves choosing between quick, surface-level work
        and larger contractors whose pricing and process don’t match the scale of
        the project. Achillea Built exists in the middle — bringing a construction
        mindset to projects that still benefit from careful execution.
      </p>

      <p class="leading-7">
        Each job is approached with attention to preparation, material selection,
        and long-term durability. The goal is not to overbuild or overcharge, but to
        make sound decisions that result in work that holds up over time.
      </p>

      <p class="leading-7">
        This means focusing on details where they matter, communicating clearly
        throughout the process, and treating each home with respect.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 reveal">
      <h2 class="mb-4">How I Work</h2>

      <div class="space-y-4 max-w-2xl">
        <p class="leading-7">
          Projects are handled directly, with clear expectations set up front and
          followed through to completion.
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Clear, straightforward estimates</li>
          <li>Thoughtful planning before work begins</li>
          <li>Clean, organized job sites</li>
          <li>Consistent communication throughout the project</li>
          <li>Work completed with long-term durability in mind</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 reveal">
      <h2 class="mb-4">A Practical Approach to Craftsmanship</h2>

      <p class="leading-7 max-w-2xl mb-4">
        Craftsmanship matters — but not as a luxury feature. The focus is on doing
        things properly, with attention to fit, finish, and the details that affect
        how the work performs over time.
      </p>

      <p class="leading-7 max-w-2xl">
        The result is work that feels considered, functions well, and fits naturally
        within the home.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 reveal">
      <h2 class="mb-4">A Good Fit</h2>

      <p class="leading-7 max-w-2xl mb-4">
        Achillea Built is a good fit for homeowners who value quality work, clear
        communication, and a straightforward process.
      </p>

      <p class="leading-7 max-w-2xl">
        If your project falls somewhere between a simple repair and a full-scale
        renovation, and you want it handled with care, it’s likely a good match.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 reveal">
      <a href="/estimate" class="btn btn-lg sm:min-w-56">
        Request an Estimate
      </a>
    </div>

  </section>
</Layout>